data.title: Law & order. Season 13
data.meta_description: Part of the longest-running brand on television. A complex drama about New York's investigative and legal team.  In 24 gut-wrenching cases, new DA Arthur Branch brings a new tough-as-nails methodology to the team that proves formidable against the wrongdoers who maim, mutilate and murder their victims. But no one is invincible, and before the season is over, more than one of New York's finest will be personally impacted by crimes that rock the headlines.
